{"tid":194333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咖啡成癮 決心戒啡Post","createTime":"2017-04-10T01:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T06:05:13.000Z","uid":95314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0619f3e11902764309920459c1d7b8f3b0c59fd0","tid":194333,"uid":95314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:36:17.000Z","msg":"啡齡12年，高峰期一日五杯。<br />\n咖啡本身同茶一樣都係提神作用，但家陣有冇精神，夠唔夠瞓都會飲，唔飲成個人囉囉攣咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戒除目的有二，一嚟去除咗呢種合法性毒品嘅癮，二嚟可以慳返唔少錢。<br />\n我粗略計過一年用响含咖啡因飲品都用咗五位數字，好多時候係心癮起去買，而唔係真係口渴或有需要提神。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日day 1 目標係堅持一年!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6a8bbec9580e246acd19a479f756d3f5d93aa9","tid":194333,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:06:42.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我咖啡因過敏 飲一杯咖啡都會嘔加全身無力 會暈"},{"pid":"e3fcfce2e6856ff064429b50689114c9a03784e6","tid":194333,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}